  "reason_thou": "1. **Understanding the Issue**: The issue arises in the `ReadDataFromGlobal` function
when attempting to extract bits from an `APInt` value using the `extractBits` method. The parameters
passed to `extractBits` are derived from `ByteOffset` and `IntBytes`. In this case, `ByteOffset` (6)
exceeds the size of the `APInt` value (5 bytes), leading to an out-of-bounds access and triggering an
assertion failure.\n\n2. **Analyzing `opt`'s Log**: The log indicates that the assertion failure occurs in
